expression in God, Christians believe God is truth itself, goodness itself, and beauty itself.\", \"from\": 6043, \"to\": 6182, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6107, \"end\": 6117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999746263901669, \"rank\": 2.537145809202397e-05, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all transcendentals\", \"from\": 6058, \"to\": 6077}, {\"ngram\": \"full expression\", \"from\": 6083, \"to\": 6098}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 6102, \"to\": 6105}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 6126, \"to\": 6129}, {\"ngram\": \"truth\", \"from\": 6133, \"to\": 6138}, {\"ngram\": \"beauty\", \"from\": 6168, \"to\": 6174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To seek beauty is to seek God.\", \"from\": 6183, \"to\": 6213, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"beauty\", \"from\": 6191, \"to\": 6197}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 6209, \"to\": 6212}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More than the visible details, however, this new religion has a different definition of God.\", \"from\": 6217, \"to\": 6309, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the visible details\", \"from\": 6227, \"to\": 6246}, {\"ngram\": \"this new religion\", \"from\": 6257, \"to\": 6274}, {\"ngram\": \"a different definition\", \"from\": 6279, \"to\": 6301}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 6305, \"to\": 6308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The god of this new religion has not been named yet.\", \"from\": 6310, \"to\": 6362, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The god\", \"from\": 6310, \"to\": 6317}, {\"ngram\": \"this new religion\", \"from\": 6321, \"to\": 6338}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Often purveyors of the new religion have tried to insert it into Christianity.\", \"from\": 6363, \"to\": 6441, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6428, \"end\": 6440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9